com.alexgilleran.icesoap.request
Interface ListRequest<ResultType,SOAPFaultType>

Type Parameters:
ResultType - The type of the object that this request will return a list of.
All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:
SOAP11ListRequest<ResultType>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ListRequestImpl, SOAP11ListRequestImpl
public interface ListRequest<ResultType,SOAPFaultType>
extends Request<List<ResultType>,SOAPFaultType>

This request deals specifically with SOAP calls that recall a list of items, allowing listeners to be bound that will be called every time a new object is parsed rather than waiting until the entire request is finished.

Author:
Alex Gilleran

registerObserver

void registerObserver(SOAPListObserver<ResultType,SOAPFaultType> observer)
Registers an observer for new item, exception and completion events. Note that registering a SOAP11ListObserver (using this method) will result in the observer receiving events on each new item - registering a SOAP11Observer with Request#registerObserver(SOAP11Observer) will only result in it receiving exception and completion.

Parameters:
observer - The observer to register.
